```
# Python bytecode cache directories
__pycache__/

# Compiled Python files
*.pyc

# Optimized Python files
*.pyo

# Environment variables file
.env

# Virtual environment directories
.venv/

# Python egg info directories
*.egg-info/

# macOS system files
.DS_Store

# Log files
*.log
```

This file, when placed in the root directory of a git repository, will ensure that the specified files and directories are ignored by git.
